Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api.association Description

Association manager API

An association manager is responsible for managing to-one and to-many associations between model types. Default implementations of this API use JavaBeans accessors and the methods of the JDK Collections API to manage associations.

If your domain model exposes is own API for managing associations between its model types, you can implement an association manager and register it with a ViewContext when applying views to update your model instances.
